{"tid":1988320,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合國關切港控15子 促守公約","createTime":"2020-04-25T06:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T08:43:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"577038e21189555b27c404642100c47b504d5846","tid":1988320,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:39:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200425/5BLB6Y2ETZEVOL7KPN62MP7RJI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200425%2F5BLB6Y2ETZEVOL7KPN62MP7RJI%2F&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=2f79ef60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200425%2F5BLB6Y2ETZEVOL7KPN62MP7RJI%2F&h=613eb943\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200425/5BLB6Y2ETZEVOL7KPN62MP7RJI/</a><br />\n<br />\n聯合國關切港控15子 促守公約<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200425/large/1587746130_287a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200425%2Flarge%2F1587746130_287a.gif&h=9844815e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民昨在和你Lunch聲援被濫捕民主派人士。何量鈞攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府上周六突然對15名民主派人士進行大搜捕，不單止引起外國政府與媒體關注，聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處昨亦表態，對事件表示密切關注，更特別提醒港府有承擔《公民權利政治權利國際公約》的義務。國際特赦組織發起聯署行動，呼籲外界去信律政司司長鄭若驊撤銷控罪。<br />\n<br />\n警方上周六突然就去年8.18、10.1及10.20的3次遊行，以組織及參與未經批准集結、遊行罪名，大舉搜捕15名民主派人士，包括民主黨創黨主席李柱銘、前法律界議員吳靄儀等，事件亦引起美國、澳洲、加拿大、比利時等多國政界人士關注。事隔近一個星期，聯合國人權事務高級專員辦事處昨透過社交網站發文，表示密切關注有關15名香港社運人士的案件，提醒港府有義務承擔《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》之餘，更明言希望港府與所有持份者接觸，為所有人的未來利益找出解決方案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特赦組織籲鄭若驊撤控<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：梁君彥尋法律意見 建制備方案<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織則發起聯署行動，呼籲外界去信律政司司長鄭若驊，對15名民主派人士被當局以《公安條例》中的罪名檢控表示關注，因為條例不符合國際人權法與和平集會權利的標準。<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織促請鄭若驊撤銷對15名民主派人士的檢控、停止起訴和平示威者、及令《公安條例》符合國際人權法和標準。<br />\n<br />\n■記者呂浩然"},{"pid":"9ca6cb23b002c65a65adc7394280f357ce8f7843","tid":1988320,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:45:25.000Z","msg":"【入黎我話你知香港點獨立】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1988323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1988323</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"317331dcb3e5392784848f5a7b65cacfa550fb55","tid":1988320,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:47:21.000Z","msg":"緊爽 : 公約已成歷史文件. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae86adbbc9e553b4c0853169147e48feceb14ff9","tid":1988320,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:17:27.000Z","msg":"香港社會運動需要轉型<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fqmBgS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fqmBgS</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixjbr30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fixjbr30.jpg&h=3dd23a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UuJC633.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUuJC633.jpg&h=bd20a436&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56a6c3905baf450123e2a49344a35f6cfa59ec12","tid":1988320,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae86adbbc9e553b4c0853169147e48feceb14ff9","tid":1988320,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:17:27.000Z","msg":"香港社會運動需要轉型<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fqmBgS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fqmBgS</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixjbr30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fixjbr30.jpg&h=3dd23a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UuJC633.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUuJC633.jpg&h=bd20a436&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:43:05.000Z","msg":"知你想講乜， 不過你物理 fail <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}